## 📌 A Note About Our Roadmap

We're now moving from "learning Flutter" to "building production-ready architecture."

This is the same approach you'll see in many professional Flutter apps:

* **models/** → Stores data.
* **screens/** → Displays data.
* **services/** (coming soon) → Handles OCR, AI, database, and cloud interactions.

Organizing the project this way now will make the later backend integration much cleaner and easier to manage.
